      "text": "It's on the lip of the gods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was 14.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was taken to camp, I was 13 and 1/2 years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through the media, through the Nazi papers, through the discussions at home-- discussions wherever you went.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you only heard Hitler or his-- his-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] senior officer speaking out in public meetings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you couldn't help but know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
